t:
I'm okay, there's nothing behind the closed door.
I'm okay, it's just the sound of the house settling.
I'm okay, I can see the light in the hallway.


I'm okay; until the door opens
on it's own.
I'm not okay, as the shadow
starts breathing and crawling.
c:
“I'm okay”, the neighbors will hear a strange growl from my house.
